<html><head><meta charset='utf-8'><title>TOEIC Results</title></head><body><h1>TOEIC SPEAKING RESULTS</h1><h3>Part 3: Technology (Q6) (ID: 65)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you think we rely too much on technology?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> I agree with that recently a lot of people depend on AI to do tasks, jobs.
Why do you think people rely (=depend) on technology. ?
Technology help the answer for question quickly. </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Holidays (Q4) (ID: 66)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What is the most important holiday in your country?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is the most important holiday in your country?
I think Tet Holiday. Tet is one of the most famous traditional holiday in Viet Nam. 
When is Tet celebrated ?. 
Tet is often celebrated at the begining of the year from Januray to February. 
What do people often prepare before Tet ?.
Before Tet people often buy a thing of thing for example, some stickers, flowers to decor your house, they buy food and drink to eat in the holiday. Some people make a plan to return back to their hometown, they buy a ticket.
What do people usually do in the morning of TET ?.
In the morning, people go to their neighbour to visit and give a wish, an pocket money.
They also go to the temple to wish for luck.
lucky *adj = luck *n
What do people often do in the evening ?.
In the evening all members in family gather togother to have small talk, they talk about what happend during the year. All member sit arround the fire to make Chung and Day Cake. they watch firework and Lan dance.
How do you feel about Tet ?.
To many people, Tet is a occasion but to me, Tet is feeling.
because i can meet my family i can talk together with other memebers so i feel very cozy and happy







 






 
