</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Learning (Q6) (ID: 71)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What is the best way to learn a new skill?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is the best way to learn a new skill?
