-> at work. -> wear basic clothes -> T-shirt or short dress -> It makes me look more formal and professional.
-> at home. -> i usually wear more comfortable clothes -> because i do not have to meet anyone so i just want to relax.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Clothes (Q5) (ID: 73)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you follow fashion trends?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you follow fashion trends?
