I prefer giving gifts because caring is sharing. (cho đi để nhận lại). i want to see their smile when they receive the give.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Gifts (Q6) (ID: 77)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What was the best gift you ever received?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What was the best gift you ever received?
