</p><hr><h3>Part 5: Opinion (ID: 96)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you agree or disagree: working in a team is better than working alone?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you agree or disagree: working in a team is better than working alone?
Not entirely. It is two-sided
