But on the negative side, the co-workers are not always good sometimes they will push their work to me, talk bad behind my back. and i think when team have too much ideas, it is hard to choos. Teamworks demand great leadership.


</p><hr><h3>Part 5: Opinion (ID: 97)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you think it is better to live in a big city or the countryside?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you think it is better to live in a big city or the countryside?
I think it is two-sided. 
In the big cỉty, you will have better job opportunity. Have life quality for example: devopling education, healthcare and transportation. 
While, in the countryside. I can live in my house with my parents and the environment is better. The air is fresh and less vehicles, traffic jams.  Everything is cheaper than in the big cỉty. Living in the countryside is healthier. the life-pacing is slower.


